# Defining the create_dataframe function
def create_dataframe(data):
    years = []
    months = []
    values = []

    for item in data:
        year = item[0][:4]
        month = item[0][4:]
        value = item[1]

        years.append(year)
        months.append(month)
        values.append(value)

    df = pd.DataFrame({'Year': years, 'Month': months, 'Value': values})
    df['Year'] = df['Year'].astype(int)
    df['Month'] = df['Month'].astype(int)

    return df
